# Aristo runtime, cache, and per-user state: never commit these.
# Durable state (.aristo/proofs/*.proof, .aristo/specs/, .aristo/feedback/,
# .aristo/expectations.toml, .aristo/canon-matches.toml, aristo.toml) is
# committed and intentionally not listed here.
.aristo/index.toml
# Per-annotation docs: normally committed, but excluded from this PR to keep the
# diff small. Regenerate with `aristo doc` (see CONTRIBUTING.md -> Aristo).
.aristo/doc/
.aristo/sessions/
.aristo/nudge-state.toml
.aristo/verify-queue/
.aristo/critique-queue/
.aristo/critiques/
.aristo/proofs/*.proof.bak
.aristo/archive/

